            <title>[LU-17137] Deprecate l_getidentity files alias</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17137</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Historically l_getidentity &apos;lookup files&apos; masks the nss &apos;files&apos; module in favor the passws/group files in /etc/lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

